{
  "stem": "15694.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Under-- under which, you know, which gave him the pretext to start the war, to march to Po-- into Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, that was particular-- I didn't know it at the time, but Gliwice, I said to my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gliwice?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it's a big town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Have you heard anything?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, we don't know of any camp or anything, but maybe there's a camp-- another camp here, a sister camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then suddenly you heard a voice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One of the passengers said, if the engine-- it was evening-- stays at the front, we'll go-- it's a good sign.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We'll go to a camp to Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If he goes to the back, it'll go to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The engine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now I have-- the Auschwitz was not anything special in my mind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, probably I've heard of it, but the moment-- the reaction of the others, who knows what it was-- I suddenly had a terrible feeling.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was a bundle-- a bundle of nerves in no time, and the nerves-- by a nervous reaction, I had sort of a-- I had a terrible need to go somewhere, and what would you do?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now it was night, and like a conjurer who wants to hide what other people shouldn't see, I managed to take sort of a tea towel out of our baggage, put it on my little place underneath me and I did what I hoped other people didn't see, and the bundle went overboard.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It belongs to the story, and that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I continue this story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, the lights in front of us were all red, and I have a whole chapter of this particular incident, 'A Night to Remember,' I called it.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
